<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Passado" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Passado,</orth> a motion forwards and thrust in fencing: <emph>the p. he</emph> (Cupid) <cit><quote>respects not,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.184" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>ah, the immortal p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 26</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>come, sir, your p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 88</bibl></cit>.
